summary:
Just recently completed my MBA, with a huge appetite for Finance; I am a sincere and goal oriented individual with sound knowledge of managing particular spectrums of Finance including purchase & procurement, logistics, project management.

Acknowledged capabilities in the implementation of Financial management systems.I have deep experience in excel, building complex models and learn quickly about new industries and markets.

Sound knowledge in Accounting, working procedures of the Fianancial Department,  people management and communication skills; Familiarity of process and system with proven ability to work independently as well as a part of a team; Multilingual with proficiency in English, French, I am open to positions the world over.
